title: The Rolling Stones - Live At The Altamont Speedway
description:
Legendary live performance by The Rolling Stones on their infamous Altamont Festival in 1969 (aka the "Killer Festival").

This recording is a very rare bootleg, I only found it here, after hours of searching and many outdated and broken links : http://www.iorr.org/talk/read.php?2,1890137,1891801.

Another reissue seems to be available here : http://www.discjapan.com/shop/rolling-stones/rolling-stones-the-altamont-speedway-free-festival-2cd-tarkl-tcd-001-12-2/

All files are .flac, stage and audience disturbances are split into tracks too. Tagged, pictures includes.

Thanks to the original makers of this bootleg!
